<div class="our-food text-center">
	<h3>OUR FOOD</h3>
	<hr>
	<p>The HAKUNA meal delivery programme is based on a diet full of fruits, vegetables, whole grains, nuts, legumes and modest intakes of animal and fish products. Our nutritional beliefs are the basis of each and every meal that is delivered to your door. 
 	</p>
