			<h6>MEAT</h6>
			<p>Meat is very rich in protein and contains Vitamin B12, which is not found in most plant foods. We use pasture – raised animals that are free from antibiotics and hormones. We like to use a variety of cuts because they are all nutritious and delicious.
			</p>
